e scalar case and work out the divergent part of the\ndS$_4$ effective action which renormalizes the cosmological correlators. We\nfind that bulk masses and wavefunction can logarithmically run as a result of\nthe dS$_4$ curvature, and that operators on the late time boundary are\nradiatively generated. More developments are needed to extract all one-loop\ninformation from the cosmological effective action.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Wed, 1 Dec 2021 19:00:01 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Tue, 3 May 2022 19:00:11 GMT"}],"update_date":"2022-07-22"}
