y demonstrates that the\ndust-induced CR confinement can be very important under certain conditions,\ne.g., the dusty circumgalactic medium around quasars or superluminous galaxies.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Wed, 1 Dec 2021 19:00:01 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Fri, 22 Apr 2022 06:48:15 GMT"}],"update_date":"2022-04-25"}
