ultaneously improve the performance of image captioning (+2.9\nCider) and grounding (+2.3 F1LOC).\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Thu, 2 Dec 2021 04:17:01 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Wed, 13 Apr 2022 01:45:46 GMT"}],"update_date":"2022-04-14"}
